    "text": "In this context, I observe that all the documents on which the Petitioner relies on to",
    "fonts": [
      "Calibri"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.960000038146973
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 6,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      511.39,
      542.71,
      524.35
    ],
    "text": "establish his appointment has been given by the Chairman or the General Manager of the",
    "fonts": [
      "Calibri"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.960000038146973
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 6,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      533.92,
      160.03,
      548.11
    ],
    "text": "1st Respondent.",
    "fonts": [
      "Calibri"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      8.520000457763672,
      12.960000038146973
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 6,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      565.72,
      542.98,
      579.94
    ],
    "text": "The 1st Respondent was established by Section 2(1) of the Western Province Provincial",
    "fonts": [
      "Calibri"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      8.520000457763672,
      12.960000038146973
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 6,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      590.86,
      542.86,
      603.82
    ],
    "text": "Road Development Authority Statute No. 04 of 1989 (Statute). In terms of Section 11(1)",
    "fonts": [
      "Calibri"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.960000038146973
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 6,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      613.39,
      542.88,
      627.58
    ],
    "text": "of the Statute, the power to appoint staff to the 1st Respondent is vested in the Provincial",
    "fonts": [
      "Calibri"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      8.520000457763672,
      12.960000038146973
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 6,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      637.15,
      543.03,
      651.34
    ],
    "text": "Public Service Commission. The Chairman or the General Manager of the 1st Respondent",
    "fonts": [
      "Calibri"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      8.520000457763672,
      12.960000038146973
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 6,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      662.26,
      542.59,
      675.22
    ],
    "text": "does not have any power to make appointments. As such, the contractual appointment",
    "fonts": [
      "Calibri"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.960000038146973
    ]
  },
